# Environment & Configuration

## Environment variables
- All config from env vars in production. `.env` for local dev (gitignored). `.env.example` committed with placeholders and comments.

## Config loading
- Single config module (`src/chimera_sdk/config/`). Pydantic `BaseSettings` for validation.
- Fail fast on missing required vars. Never scatter `os.getenv()` — all access through config module.

## Environments
- `development` — local, debug logging, relaxed limits.
- `staging` — mirrors production, synthetic data, full observability.
- `production` — strict validation, secret manager, no debug logging.
- Set via `CHIMERA_ENV` variable.
